# Global Graph Write Scope Rule

## Critical Constraint

Agents must NOT modify code outside:


/global-graph


Allowed changes:

- graph schema
- graph builder
- graph queries
- graph indexing
- graph retrieval logic

Disallowed:

- ingestion pipeline changes
- backend service redesign
- frontend changes
- infrastructure changes

If changes outside `/global-graph` are required:


STOP
REQUEST HUMAN APPROVAL


This rule protects the stability of the main system.